    <section id="about">
      <h1>Welcome to WeDeserve Freedom</h1>
      <p>Our platform is dedicated to empowering women affected by domestic violence and providing them with the support they need to break free from abusive relationships through a process that combines mental health and financial education.</p>
    </section>
    <section id="features">
      <h2>Key Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Secure and confidential platform</li>
        <li>Access to mental health resources</li>
        <li>Educational resources for financial empowerment</li>
        <li>Community support and networking</li>
        <li>Verified professionals for legal and social assistance</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section id="vision">
      <h2>Our Vision</h2>
      <p>At WeDeserve Freedom, we envision a world where every woman has the opportunity to break free from the cycle of domestic violence. By utilizing the Web3 infrastructure and the power of blockchain, we aim to create a decentralized platform that ensures privacy, security, and autonomy for our users.</p>
    </section>
    <section id="blockchain">
      <h2>How Blockchain Transforms our Platform</h2>
      <p>Blockchain technology forms the foundation of our platform, enabling us to establish a secure and transparent environment for our users. By leveraging blockchain in the Web3 ecosystem, we can provide tamper-proof record-keeping, verifiable identities, and privacy-enhancing features to ensure the confidentiality and integrity of user data.</p>
    </section>
    <section id="team">
